## Onboarding Workflow
1. Create tenant IAM role with inline policy (policy version managed)
2. Tag role with `tenant_id`
3. Add tenant prefix to S3 bucket policy
4. Enable CloudTrail for audit trail

## Offboarding/Revocation (<15 min)
1. `aws iam delete-access-key` for all active keys
2. `aws iam update-role --max-session-duration 1` (forces STS re-auth)
3. Deny attached policy with explicit `Deny` override
4. CloudWatch Events rule triggers Lambda to update S3 bucket policy
5. DynamoDB: Attach SCP deny policy to tenant OU

## Rollback Strategy
1. CloudTrail query: `aws cloudtrail lookup-events --lookup-attributes AttributeKey=Username,AttributeValue=<tenant-id>`
2. Revert IAM policy via `aws iam create-policy-version --set-as-default`
3. Emergency: Admin override role bypasses tenant tags
4. S3: Re-add Allow statement via AWS Config rollback

