| **4. Non-TLS connection** | Attempt PUT over HTTP | S3 bucket policy denies request |
| **5. KMS key access by untagged role** | Role without tenant-id tag attempts encryption | KMS policy denies encryption |
| **6. Public access attempt** | Attempt to access bucket publicly | Bucket policy denies - no public access enforced |
| **7. Session tag verification** | Verify STS passes tenant-id as session tag | CloudTrail shows aws:PrincipalTag/tenant-id matches aws:SessionTag/tenant-id |
| **8. Parquet file verification** | Write and read back Parquet files | Files correctly partitioned by date and tenant |

## Why This Is Asked

